{"tid":2475250,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月足球番】再見了，我的克拉默","createTime":"2021-04-04T14:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T20:09:56.000Z","uid":4618,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"da795621f2f35c89204e2b36bc9e28a2248e2b11","tid":2475250,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY79SQj4W5fdsu7r6STUPEw29fYoeKMzoD43GVmBJkQLA?filename=mX5C5Bn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmX5C5Bn.jpg&h=45ef4138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV7VwQdnVuqnQeM3bpXb3otFcx4ocDdYXBTpvr2uZSgDw?filename=qUArYW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUArYW3.jpg&h=6383a787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由 新川直司所創作的漫畫《再見了，我的克拉默》，宣布將推出電視動畫，於2021年4月開播。<br />\n<br />\n周防堇在國中是女子足球隊的翼鋒，有著驚人的足球天分。但由於其他同學跟不上她的程度，導致球隊每年都在地區大賽中敗退。即將從國中畢業時，她在球場上的對手曾志崎綠邀她等上高中後一起踢球，原本曾志崎綠想加入足球強校浦和邦成，但周防堇卻因為「某個原因」而選擇弱小的蕨青南高。之後，從前的知名女子職業足球選手「生剝鬼能見」來到蕨青南高擔任教練，她們之間將會擦出什麼樣的火花&hellip;&hellip;?<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aMZSgEEv-Io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaMZSgEEv-Io&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=bd5bd882\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aMZSgEEv-Io</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w35siyx840U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw35siyx840U&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=441a8297\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w35siyx840U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kim1S3ySNqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkim1S3ySNqs&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=7d6086a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kim1S3ySNqs</a><br />\n<br />\n劇場版PV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l7JeC7N9gH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl7JeC7N9gH8&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=88530e6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l7JeC7N9gH8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>STAFF</strong><br />\n原作：新川直司「さよならフットボール」<br />\n監督：宅野誠起<br />\n腳本：高橋ナツコ<br />\n角色設計：伊藤依織子<br />\n音樂：横山克<br />\n動畫制作：ライデンフィルム<br />\n<br />\n<strong>CAST</strong><br />\n恩田希：島袋美由利<br />\n越前佐和：若山詩音<br />\n周防すみれ：黒沢ともよ<br />\n曽志崎緑：悠木碧<br />\n白鳥綾：古城門志帆<br />\n田勢恵梨子：嶋村侑<br />\n宮坂真琴：山田麻莉奈<br />\n菊池類：前田玲奈<br />\n岸歩：和氣あず未<br />\n小紫沙織：酒井美沙乃<br />\n御徒町紀子：春野杏<br />\n加古川香梨奈：長谷川玲奈<br />\n能見奈緒子：甲斐田裕子<br />\n深津吾朗：諏訪部順一<br />\n梶みずき：早見沙織<br />\n井藤春名：石川由依<br />\n佃真央：小市眞琴<br />\n桐島千花：牧野由依<br />\n天馬夕：小林愛香<br />\n安達太良アリス：きそひろこ<br />\n花房圭：大森日雅<br />\n山田鉄二：内山昂輝<br />\n竹井薫：逢坂良太<br />\n谷安昭：土屋神葉<br />\n飛鳥永建：黒田崇矢<br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://sayonara-cramer.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsayonara-cramer.com&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=bb1a8cbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://sayonara-cramer.com</a>"},{"pid":"1f02b9f7f3bb482cb9a8e441dc3f2a4bcfd7241c","tid":2475250,"uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"又到了4月的季節<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a825eded6ad0530db935ea2fb663b679c10df9e","tid":2475250,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"恩田希呢套nerf咗<br />\n本身男子學界level"},{"pid":"78b5321573e09e0cf0b27a80611f56b1c26caff3","tid":2475250,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a825eded6ad0530db935ea2fb663b679c10df9e","tid":2475250,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"恩田希呢套nerf咗<br />\n本身男子學界level"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"劇場版不g幾時有得看"},{"pid":"4ae682c6a45f73c96cb648395b65bf8224ced651","tid":2475250,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a825eded6ad0530db935ea2fb663b679c10df9e","tid":2475250,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike"